rows.label: qst101104_msg0003
rows.name:
Da must be worried sick...
I'm going back to town!

rows.label: qst101104_msg0004
rows.name:
Oh, I'll be fine. I wrapped some
cloth around my ankle, see?

rows.label: qst101104_msg0005
rows.name:
I'm sure Da will want to reward
your kindness, so make sure to
stop by when you're in town!

rows.label: qst101104_msg0101
rows.name:
Yowww... Oh! It's the
Confusion Ivy guys!

rows.label: qst101104_msg0102
rows.name:
I, uh...I ran before I
could walk, so my ankle's
all messed up again...

rows.label: qst101104_msg0201
rows.name: Sorry for making you do my job...

rows.label: qst101104_msg0202
rows.name: I'll have to toughen up, huh...

rows.label: qst101104_msg0301
rows.name:
You brought some Gulan
Walnut! Thank you so much!

rows.label: qst101104_msg0302
rows.name:
And just when my ankle
got better, too...
